OL,3,CMillions take to roads as Storm Dave
OL,4,Ccauses windy Easter weekend
OL,6,FMillions of travellers are taking to
OL,7,Fthe road ahead of a windy Easter
OL,8,Fweekend with Storm Dave forecast to
OL,9,Fbring gusts of up to 90mph.
OL,11,FTravel trade organisation Abta
OL,12,Festimated that two million people from
OL,13,Fthe UK will travel abroad between Good
OL,14,FFriday and Easter Monday, as the RAC
OL,15,Fpredicted it would be the busiest
OL,16,FEaster on the roads since 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
