OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775221865
OL,3,CMillions take to roads as Storm Dave
OL,4,Ccauses windy Easter weekend
OL,6,FThe Met Office has issued yellow
OL,7,Fweather warnings for wind covering the
OL,8,Fwhole of mainland Scotland, Northern
OL,9,FIreland, parts of northern England and
OL,10,FNorth Wales from Saturday into Sunday.
OL,12,FOil prices ` which have a significant
OL,13,Feffect on the cost of wholesale fuel `
OL,14,Fhave soared in response to Iran's
OL,15,Fstranglehold on tankers passing
OL,16,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,18,FThe RAC said the average price of a
OL,19,Flitre of diesel at UK forecourts on
OL,20,FWednesday was 184.2p, up 29% since the
OL,21,Fwar started on February 28.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
