OL,3,CMillions take to roads as Storm Dave
OL,4,Ccauses windy Easter weekend
OL,6,FAverage petrol prices have reached
OL,7,F153.7p per litre, a rise of 16% over
OL,8,Fthe same period.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FForecasters warned there is a chance
OL,16,Fof "injuries and danger to life" from
OL,17,Fflying debris while the strong winds
OL,18,Fmay also cause some damage and travel
OL,19,Fdisruption.
