OL,3,CMillions take to roads as Storm Dave
OL,4,Ccauses windy Easter weekend
OL,6,FScotland will be hit by the strongest
OL,7,Fgusts, which could be up to 80-90mph
OL,8,Ffor a short time in exposed locations.
OL,10,FA yellow warning of snow has also been
OL,11,Fissued for north-west Scotland where
OL,12,Fsome places could see 10-20cm.
OL,14,FA yellow warning of wind will be in
OL,15,Fforce across mainland Scotland from
OL,16,F6pm on Saturday until midday on Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
