OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775221865
OL,3,CMillions take to roads as Storm Dave
OL,4,Ccauses windy Easter weekend
OL,6,FThe warning covering northern England
OL,7,Fand North Wales will be in place from
OL,8,F5pm on Saturday until 7am on Sunday
OL,9,Fwhile Northern Ireland will be covered
OL,10,Fby a warning from 2pm on Saturday
OL,11,Funtil 2am the following day.
OL,13,FThe snow warning in northern Scotland
OL,14,Fwill be valid from 3pm on Saturday
OL,15,Funtil 3am on Sunday.
OL,17,FForecasters said that southern parts
OL,18,Fof the UK will not feel the impact of
OL,19,Fthe storm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
