OL,3,CMillions take to roads as Storm Dave
OL,4,Ccauses windy Easter weekend
OL,6,FThose travelling in Scotland over the
OL,7,Fweekend were warned to expect
OL,8,Fpotential delays to their journeys.
OL,10,FGeorge Fiddes, from Transport
OL,11,FScotland, said: "Storm Dave is a
OL,12,Ftimely reminder that we can face
OL,13,Fchallenging weather conditions at any
OL,14,Ftime of year, not just during the
OL,15,Fwinter period.
OL,26,@sD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
