CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775221865
OL,3,CMillions take to roads as Storm Dave
OL,4,Ccauses windy Easter weekend
OL,6,F"The Met Office warnings show high
OL,7,Fwinds will impact the whole country
OL,8,Fthis weekend, with the prospect of
OL,9,Fsome areas also being affected by
OL,10,Fheavy rain and snow, so I'm urging
OL,11,Fpeople to plan ahead if they are
OL,12,Ftravelling over the Easter period.
OL,14,F"Motorists should check their planned
OL,15,Froutes before setting off."
OL,17,FPolice in Scotland urged HGV and bus
OL,18,Fdrivers to use "extreme caution" when
OL,19,FStorm Dave hits at the weekend.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUwD@[O]zD@POUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
