OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775221865
OL,3,CMillions take to roads as Storm Dave
OL,4,Ccauses windy Easter weekend
OL,6,FSteve Gooding, director of the RAC
OL,7,FFoundation, said: "For those driving
OL,8,Fon the continent this Easter it is a
OL,9,Fcase of out of the frying pan and into
OL,10,Fthe fire.
OL,12,F"If pump prices are high here ` and
OL,13,Findeed they are ` then in many parts
OL,14,Fof Europe they have gone through the
OL,15,Froof, including in France.
OL,17,F"It might seem counterintuitive, but
OL,18,Ffilling up at Dover rather than in
OL,19,FCalais could be the wise option."
OL,26,@oD@SOUtD@AOUyD@AOU{D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
