OL,3,CMillions take to roads as Storm Dave
OL,4,Ccauses windy Easter weekend
OL,6,FNational Highways said it will lift
OL,7,F1,500 miles of roadworks from its
OL,8,Fnetwork of motorways and major A roads
OL,9,Fin England between Thursday and Easter
OL,10,FMonday to ease journeys.
OL,12,FUK holidaymakers jetting off to the
OL,13,FEuropean Union are being warned to
OL,14,Fexpect two-hour delays on arrival as
OL,15,Fcountries are ramping up the
OL,16,Fdeployment of a new border system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
