OL,3,CMillions take to roads as Storm Dave
OL,4,Ccauses windy Easter weekend
OL,6,FThe EU's Entry Exit System involves
OL,7,Fpeople from third-party countries such
OL,8,Fas the UK having their fingerprints
OL,9,Fregistered and photograph taken to
OL,10,Fenter the Schengen Area, which
OL,11,Fconsists of 29 European countries,
OL,12,Fmainly in the EU.
OL,14,FTrade body Airports Council
OL,15,FInternational said the latest data
OL,16,Fcollected from airports across Europe
OL,17,Fshows a "continued deterioration in
OL,18,Fwaiting times at border crossing
OL,19,Fpoints".
OL,26,@yD@IOU{D@GO]
